BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:<a href="https://tfl.gov.uk/tube-dlr-overground/status/?Input=&lineIds=&dateTypeSelect=Future%20date&direction=&startDate=2026-06-25T21:10:30&endDate=2026-06-26T00:29:00">Disruption map.</a>\n\nSevere delays between Hayes & Harlington and Heathrow Terminals due to infrastructure damage caused by extreme weather. London Underground are accepting tickets via any reasonable route. Please use the Piccadilly line to travel between Heathrow Airport and Central London. If you are travelling between terminals\, a bus service operates between Heathrow Terminals 2&3\, 4 and 5. GOOD SERVICE on the rest of the line.  
